"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?11/49/12058?source=see_link\">",
"      Hematopoietic cell transplantation in follicular lymphoma",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?9/40/9865?source=see_link\">",
